<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <!-- Required meta tags -->
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta

    name="viewport"
    content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no"
    />
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/public/main.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/public/sirius.css" />
    <script src="../public/sirius.js" defer></script>
    <script src="../public/header.js" defer></script>
    <script
      src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/c3d18ec51c.js"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    ></script>
    <title>Moggle Labs</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <%if(사용자 === undefined){ %> <%- include('header.html') %> <%}%>
    <%if(사용자!==undefined){%> <%- include('header-login.html') %> <%}%>
    
    <div id="body">
      <div id="wrap">
        <section>
          <article>
            <h3>시리우스</h3>
            <p>재무 데이터 기반의 팩터 추출 엔진입니다.</p>
            <p>아직 베타 버전인 만큼, 앞으로 더 많은 기능들이 추가될 예정입니다.</p>
            <br/>
            <p>추가되었으면 하는 기능이 있다면 moggle.labs@gmail.com으로 문의주시면 감사하겠습니다.</p>
            <form action="/sirius" method="POST" class="form-box">

              <div class="select-box">
                <p>펙터 재료</p>
                <select
                name="factor"
                class="select-factor"
                oninput="document.getElementById('value1').innerHTML=this.value;"
                >
                <option value="시가총액">시가총액</option>
                <option value="매출액">매출액</option>
                <option value="영업이익">영업이익</option>
                <option value="당기순이익">당기순이익</option>
                <option value="PER">PER</option>
                <option value="PBR">PBR</option>
                <option value="ROE">ROE</option>
                <option value="영업이익률">영업이익률</option>
                <option value="당기순이익률">당기순이익률</option>
                <option value="ROA">ROA</option>
                <option value="부채비율">부채비율</option>
              </select>
            </div>
            
              <div class="range-box">
                <p>기준점 설정</p>
                <div class="slider">
                  <input
                  type="range"
                  id="input-left"
                  name="rangeL"
                  min="0"
                  max="100"
                  value="0"
                  oninput="document.getElementById('value2').innerHTML=this.value;"
                  />
                  <input
                  type="range"
                  id="input-right"
                  name="rangeR"
                  min="1"
                  max="100"
                  value="100"
                  oninput="document.getElementById('value3').innerHTML=this.value;"
                  />
                  <div class="track">
                    <div class="range"></div>
<!--                    <div class="thumb left"></div>-->
<!--                    <div class="thumb right"></div>-->
                  </div>
                </div>
                <br />
                <p>팩터 기준점:</p>
                <p id="value2">0</p> - <p id="value3">100</p>
<!--                <br />-->
<!--                <p>팩터 기준점 상한:</p>-->
<!--                <p id="value3">100</p>-->
                <br />
                </div>
              <div class="method-box">
                <p>유니버스 설정</p>
                <br/>
                <input
                  class="method-button"
                  type="radio"
                  name="type"
                  value="전체 상장기업"
                  oninput="document.getElementById('value1').innerHTML=this.value;"
                />
                <p>전체 상장기업</p>
                <br />
                <input
                  class="method-button"
                  type="radio"
                  name="type"
                  value="KOSPI"
                  oninput="document.getElementById('value1').innerHTML=this.value;"
                />
                <p>KOSPI</p>
                <br />
                <input
                  class="method-button"
                  type="radio"
                  name="type"
                  value="KOSDAQ"
                  oninput="document.getElementById('value1').innerHTML=this.value;"
                />
                <p>KOSDAQ</p>
                <br />
              </div>
              <br />
              <button class="send-button" type="submit">전략적용</button>
            </form>
            <!-- @@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@ -->
<!-- <%= 개인 %> -->
            <iframe name="chart" class="chart-plot" src="/chart/<%= 개인 %>">
            </iframe>

            <!-- @@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@ -->
          </article>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>

    <%- include('footer.html') %>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/jquery@3.5.1/dist/jquery.min.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
